/home/citadel
citadel@citadel:~₿ sudo ln -s /home/citadel/findtx/findtx.sh /usr/local/bin/findtx
citadel@citadel:~₿ findtx
Error: no tx hash provided

USAGE: findtx <tx_hash>
The tx_hash is the hash of the transaction on the bitcoin blockchain.
